  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study will try to answer the question of whether early treatment with levothyroxine at 4
      weeks after radioactive iodine for Graves'disease will prevent overt hypothyroidism (low
      thyroid hormone levels).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
